🎯 Purpose of Section 2

This section grounds the reader in why enterprise delivery is a fundamentally different game.
It must communicate the character, constraints, and systemic pressures of large, bureaucratic customers.
Because unless the reader understands the environment, all subsequent guidance (rituals, dashboards, contracts) can feel artificial or misaligned.

In short: this section builds the lens through which the rest of the manual will be interpreted.

